'''Gobolka-Booqasho'''

Booqashada dawladu waa booqasho rasmi ah oo uu madax u yahay waddan shisheeye, martiqaadka madaxwaynaha dalka, iyada oo kan dambe uu sidoo kale u matalayo marti-geliyaha rasmiga ah ee muddada booqasho ee gobolka. Marka laga hadlayo martida, waxaa badanaa la yiraahdaa soo dhaweynta gobolka. Booqashooyinka dawlad-goboleedyada waxaa loo tixgelinayaa in ay yihiin muujinta ugu sareysa ee xiriirka saaxiibtinimo ee labada dal ee u dhaxeeya labada dal, guud ahaanna waxaa lagu tilmaamaa inay xooga saarayaan xafladaha rasmiga ah ee dadweynaha.
Booqashooyinka aan rasmiga aheyn ee aan ka ahayn booqasho dawladeed oo waddanka kale ah oo xooga saaraya munaasabadaha xafladaha, oo ah madaxa dawladda ama madaxa dawladda, ayaa lagu kala saari karaa (sida hoos udhaca miisaanka) sida booqasho rasmi ah, booqasho shaqo, booqasho khaas ah, ama booqasho marti ah Dawlada 
